## Security and compatibility

No dependency, workflow, permission, package-resolution, or version changes. `OPENAI_REALTIME_URL` accepts only `ws://` or `wss://`; documentation warns that the configured API key is sent to that endpoint. There are no credential storage or logging changes, and default behavior remains the OpenAI Realtime endpoint.
